WOOD et al., Respondents, v. CORNELL, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Otis E. Wood and others, trustees, against Alonzo B. Cornell.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Interlocutory judgment affirmed, with costs.
